<div class="page-header">
  <h1>Sonic Identity</h1>
  <p class="lead">Sound is 50% of the experience. Every sound should feel inevitable, warm, supportive, and memorable.</p>
</div>

<section class="section" id="philosophy">
  <h2>Sound Philosophy</h2>
  <div class="philosophy-grid">
    <div class="principle-card">
      <h4>Feel Inevitable</h4>
      <p>Like it couldn't be any other way</p>
    </div>
    <div class="principle-card">
      <h4>Convey Warmth</h4>
      <p>Even functional sounds feel human</p>
    </div>
    <div class="principle-card">
      <h4>Support, Not Distract</h4>
      <p>Audio serves the experience</p>
    </div>
    <div class="principle-card">
      <h4>Create Memory</h4>
      <p>Sounds become associated with feelings</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h3>Sonic References</h3>
  <ul class="reference-list">
    <li><strong>Ólafur Arnalds</strong> - Warm piano, gentle electronics, breathing space</li>
    <li><strong>Max Richter</strong> - Emotional depth, cinematic restraint</li>
    <li><strong>Nils Frahm</strong> - Organic imperfection, felt piano hammers</li>
    <li><strong>Apple</strong> - Functional clarity, satisfying feedback</li>
    <li><strong>Studio Ghibli</strong> - Whimsy without excess, natural sounds</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Not Ferni</h3>
  <div class="anti-patterns">
    <span class="tag forbidden">Clinical beeps</span>
    <span class="tag forbidden">Aggressive notifications</span>
    <span class="tag forbidden">Generic UI sounds</span>
    <span class="tag forbidden">Synthesized without humanity</span>
    <span class="tag forbidden">Loud or startling</span>
    <span class="tag forbidden">Emotionally manipulative</span>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section" id="core-elements">
  <h2>Core Sonic Elements</h2>

  <div class="core-sound-grid">
    <div class="sound-card featured">
      <div class="sound-visual">
        <div class="note-display">C4</div>
        <div class="frequency">261.63 Hz</div>
      </div>
      <h3>The Ferni Note</h3>
      <p class="description">The foundational sound of Ferni's identity</p>
      <ul class="specs">
        <li><strong>Note:</strong> Middle C - Universal, grounding</li>
        <li><strong>Timbre:</strong> Warm piano with soft felt, slight reverb</li>
        <li><strong>Character:</strong> Like a breath, not a strike</li>
        <li><strong>Duration:</strong> 800ms</li>
        <li><strong>Decay:</strong> Natural</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="sound-card">
      <div class="sound-visual">
        <div class="chord-display">Cmaj7</div>
      </div>
      <h3>Warmth Pad</h3>
      <p class="description">Ambient undertone for presence</p>
      <ul class="specs">
        <li><strong>Notes:</strong> C4, E4, G4, B4</li>
        <li><strong>Character:</strong> Barely noticeable, subconscious comfort</li>
        <li><strong>Volume:</strong> -24 dB</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="sound-card">
      <div class="sound-visual breathing">
        <div class="breath-cycle"></div>
      </div>
      <h3>The Breath</h3>
      <p class="description">Organic rhythm element</p>
      <ul class="specs">
        <li><strong>Sound:</strong> Soft inhale/exhale texture</li>
        <li><strong>Character:</strong> Not literal breath, but the feeling</li>
        <li><strong>Cycle:</strong> 500ms inhale → 200ms hold → 500ms exhale</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

